data.description:
HIGHLY REGARDED BRICK RANCH CONVENIENT TO QUAINT DOWNTOWN WEST JEFFERSON WITH A HARD TO FIND 3 CAR GARAGE AND ALL IT HAS TO OFFER. DINING, SHOPPING, BANKING ALL AT YOUR FINGERTIPS. EASY ACCESS TO SCHOOLS, CHURCHES AND HIGHWAYS. GLEAMING WOOD FLOORS INVITE YOU IN TO STAY AND MAKE THIS YOUR FOREVER HOME. ENJOY FRESH MOUNTAIN AIR AND ENTERTAINING ON THE DECK. PLENTY OF CLOSET /STORAGE SPACE.
KITCHEN FEATURES SOLID COUNTERS, UPDATED APPLIANCES AND WOOD CABINETS. EACH BRIGHT, SPACIOUS, FRESHLY PAINTED BEDROOM HAS ITS OWN LIGHTED CLOSET. CENTRAL VACUUM. LARGE LAUNDRY AREA IN BASEMENT INCLUDES WASHER AND DRYER. TWO CAR ATTACHED GARAGE WITH SHOP AREA. THIRD GARAGE IN BASEMENT ALONG WITH PLENTY OF ROOM FOR THE CAR ENTHUSIEST OR CRAFTSMAN TO SET UP SHOP.  ADDITIONAL NEW 16 x 10 OUTBUILDING FOR ENDLESS POSSIBILITIES. NEW OIL TANK.  WORTH A CLOSER LOOK.
